Interface ValorMatriz

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, operacion, Operador, Sentencias, valor, ValorComplejo
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ValorMatrizImpl

    public interface ValorMatriz
extends ValorComplejo
    A representation of the model object 'Valor Matriz'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Nombre matriz
    • Campo
    • Primer Indice
    • Segundo Indice
